.TH "vmw_fops_poll" 9 "vmw_fops_poll" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
vmw_fops_poll \- wrapper around the drm_poll function
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "__poll_t" vmw_fops_poll
.BI "(struct file *filp "  ","
.BI "struct poll_table_struct *wait "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "filp" 12
See the linux fops poll documentation.
.IP "wait" 12
See the linux fops poll documentation.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Wrapper around the drm_poll function that makes sure the device is
processing the fifo if drm_poll decides to wait.
